
This package contains several perl utilities as follows:

  xdg-traymenu  - An XDG compliant menu that sits in the system tray.

  xdg-menugen   - An XDG compliant command line root menu generator
		  for a wide list of lightweight window managers.

  xdg-icon	- An XDG compliant command line icon lookup tool.

  Also included is a set of XDG perl modules that can be used for
  building your own menus or that you can modify to support more
  window managers.

  See the manual pages for more information.
